OL,3,CRising Scams: What You Need To Know
OL,5,FBritain is facing a fraud emergency:
OL,6,Frecord numbers of us are being
OL,7,Ftargeted by scammers who are using
OL,8,Fever more sophisticated tactics to get
OL,9,Fhold of our money, with an estimated
OL,10,F#9.4 billion stolen last year.
OL,12,FWith fraud currently accounting for
OL,13,F44% of all reported crime, it seems
OL,14,Fthat no corner of our lives are safe
OL,15,Ffrom the clutches of fraudsters.
OL,16,FTonight met the victims of some of
OL,17,Fthese increasingly sophisticated scams.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
