OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772197440
OL,3,CRising Scams: What You Need To Know
OL,5,FBuilding trust is the cornerstone to
OL,6,Fpersuading someone to part with their
OL,7,Fcash, something wellbeing therapist
OL,8,FNancy knows only too well. Back in
OL,9,F2023 she had inheritance money she was
OL,10,Flooking to invest in social housing
OL,11,Fand discovered a firm called Unique
OL,12,FProperty Investment Group, which
OL,13,Fseemed like the perfect opportunity.
OL,15,FNancy told Tonight "I just wanted my
OL,16,Finheritance to work harder for my
OL,17,Fretirement. The fact they were working
OL,18,Fwith social housing and assisted
OL,19,Fliving projects really appealed to me."
OL,26,@wD@TOU{D@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772197440
OL,3,CRising Scams: What You Need To Know
OL,5,FShe initially invested #13,000: "They
OL,6,Fsent me amazing professional
OL,7,Fbrochures, anybody looking at it would
OL,8,Fbelieve that it was a genuine
OL,9,Finvestment". The company claimed to
OL,10,Fhave links with government
OL,11,Fdepartments, the NHS and even housing
OL,12,Fproviders like YMCA.
OL,14,FEverything was going well, Nancy was
OL,15,Freceiving monthly payments and regular
OL,16,Fupdates from the firm, she decided to
OL,17,Finvest a further #15,000. But just
OL,18,Fweeks later the company entered into
OL,19,Fadministration: "When I got the email,
OL,20,FI think I went into shock."
OL,26,@mD@aOUqD@KO]{D@QOU|D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772197440
OL,3,CRising Scams: What You Need To Know
OL,5,FDespite the slick marketing, the
OL,6,Fadministrators report showed that
OL,7,Falthough investors like Nancy put over
OL,8,F#12.5 million into the company, it had
OL,9,Fjust two properties worth a little
OL,10,Fover #300,000, and Nancy's money was
OL,11,Fnowhere to be seen. She says: "I have
OL,12,Fmoments where I can't get up in the
OL,13,Fmorning. I think they saw somebody
OL,14,Fthat was vulnerable, gullible and they
OL,15,Fdidn't care"
OL,26,@sD@_OUwD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
