OL,3,CRising Scams: What You Need To Know
OL,5,FNancy along with a host of other
OL,6,Finvestors' cases have been taken on by
OL,7,FRefundee, who have already started to
OL,8,Fsee promising results from the
OL,9,FFinancial Ombudsman Service, who have
OL,10,Fruled that one case was already being
OL,11,Fviewed as authorised push payment
OL,12,Ffraud.
OL,14,FUnique told Tonight that "to the best
OL,15,Fof the directors understanding at the
OL,16,Ftime, the independent housing
OL,17,Fproviders they worked with held public-
OL,18,Fsector contracts" and their role "was
OL,19,Flimited to property sourcing and
OL,20,Frelated commercial activity."
OL,26,@vD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
