PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772197440
OL,3,CRising Scams: What You Need To Know
OL,5,FThey also told the programme
OL,6,F"investors were required to complete
OL,7,Frisk acknowledgements, including
OL,8,Fsophisticated investor self-
OL,9,Fcertification where applicable".
OL,10,FUnique also deny any wrong-doing and
OL,11,Fsay "financial and operational
OL,12,Fpressures" were a contributing factor
OL,13,Fto the company going into
OL,14,Fadministration and that "steps were
OL,15,Ftaken to stabilise the Company's
OL,16,Fposition where possible".
OL,26,@sD@EOUtD@JO]vD@YOUxD@XO]
