OL,3,CRising Scams: What You Need To Know
OL,5,FAs purchase scams increase, there has
OL,6,Falso been an influx of websites using
OL,7,FAI in ways that can be deceptive, even
OL,8,Fcreating fake pictures of the business
OL,9,Fowners. With the internet awash with
OL,10,Ffakery, some legitimate UK businesses
OL,11,Fare getting caught up in the crossfire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
