CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772197440
OL,3,CRising Scams: What You Need To Know
OL,5,FStevie has been running handmade
OL,6,Fjewellery firm Scarlett Jewellery in
OL,7,FBrighton for 28 years. However, last
OL,8,Fsummer she suddenly started receiving
OL,9,Funsolicited messages from supposed
OL,10,Fcustomers. She told Tonight 'I got an
OL,11,Fitem of jewellery in the post that
OL,12,Fwasn't made by me requesting a refund
OL,13,Fand I just thought this person had
OL,14,Fsent it to me by accident.'
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772197440
OL,3,CRising Scams: What You Need To Know
OL,5,FLittle did Stevie know that a website
OL,6,Fnamed Scarlett Jewels based in Hong
OL,7,FKong, was also selling jewellery. The
OL,8,Fwebsite claimed it was having a sale
OL,9,Fbecause the owner was retiring. This
OL,10,Fsupposedly retiring jeweller doesn't
OL,11,Factually exist, AI was being used to
OL,12,Fcreate a totally fictional jeweller,
OL,13,Fand selling sub standard products.
OL,14,FStevie said: "The jewellery is
OL,15,Fgenerally really light in weight, I'm
OL,16,Fnot sure what it's made of, but it's
OL,17,Fdefinitely not silver or gold. To be
OL,18,Fassociated with this is just
OL,19,Finsulting." When shopping online
OL,20,Fconsumers should always look out for
OL,21,Freviews from trusted sources and check
OL,22,Fthe legitimacy of the firms.
OL,26,@vD@NOU{D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
