OL,3,CRising Scams: What You Need To Know
OL,5,FPaying by credit or debit card is
OL,6,Fgenerally considered safer than paying
OL,7,Fby bank transfer, but even here
OL,8,Fcriminals are targeting even the most
OL,9,Feveryday scenarios. It's something Joe
OL,10,Ffrom Huddersfield fell foul of in
OL,11,FDecember 2024. He was visiting one of
OL,12,Fhis usual car parks in Leeds for a
OL,13,FChristmas trip to the cinema and after
OL,14,Fscanning the QR code to pay, Joe
OL,15,Fdidn't think any more of it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772197440
OL,3,CRising Scams: What You Need To Know
OL,5,FHalf an hour later, he received a call
OL,6,Ffrom his bank, he said he was told
OL,7,Fsomeone had attempted to buy #500
OL,8,Fworth of gift cards. But whilst he was
OL,9,Fon the phone to the bank, he says he
OL,10,Fwas told the scammers had tried to
OL,11,Fpurchase another #500 worth of gift
OL,12,Fcards.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772197440
OL,3,CRising Scams: What You Need To Know
OL,5,FJoe told Tonight 'I was a bit shocked,
OL,6,Fto be honest, because when you say the
OL,7,Fscam, it's somebody wanting credit
OL,8,Fcard details or a dodgy link, you
OL,9,Fdon't always think about it when
OL,10,Fyou're out and about.' Fortunately,
OL,11,FJoe's bank was able to block the
OL,12,Ftransactions and he says the QR code
OL,13,Fwas then quickly taken down by the car
OL,14,Fpark provider.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772197440
OL,3,CRising Scams: What You Need To Know
OL,5,FConsumer group Which? told the
OL,6,Fprogramme "If you're parking your car
OL,7,Fand see a QR code on the machine,
OL,8,Ffirstly take a very close look, if you
OL,9,Fare seeing one sticker over another
OL,10,Fsticker that's a big cause for
OL,11,Fconcern. And if in doubt find the
OL,12,Fgenuine firm that the machine is
OL,13,Fregistered to and give them a call".
OL,15,FHELP AND ADVICE
